# ===== ISO 80000-4:2006 Quantities and units — Part 4: Mechanics =====

# 4-1 mass
:Mass
	rdfs:label "mass"@en ;
	rdf:type owl:Class , ssmeta:MainClass , lci:PhysicalQuantityKind ;
